metadata.name: Moon Man Sir
metadata.description:
Moon Man Sir has finally agreed to be in the spotlight for us humans. He has been travelling through different dimensions in the Metaverse all through this while. For most, he went out to provide his multi-dimensional friends with amazing stuff from his planet- Moon.

Moon Man emerges from the thought of a multi-dimensional being trying to absorb human experiences and emotions, bringing all of us closer, in our joys and sorrows. 1111 uniquely hand-drawn limited collectibles straight from the heart of the artist. This is a community-driven project. 

All NFTs give access to the Moon Man Sirverse (pun intended) where everyone is welcomed with pure love and of course goodies that come along. Peace.
